      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ghent_(CDP)%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Before settlers, the Mahican people called the area Squampamock, Scom‑pa‑muck, or Squampanoc.",
